    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-808f-ad09-defd30e2eae4",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Around 11% of EU young adults end up droppoing out of tertiary-education, thus prediting early should be regarded as a priority. Deep learning models, powered by CNNs have been shown to contribute significantly to more accurate models. The study in question takes administrtative data from 6000 students and results show an accuracy of 67% in dropout for first-year students and 94% for third-year students.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1914750c-f3ba-808f-ad09-defd30e2eae4",
